<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق ر ظ:</span> <span class="c2">(الْقَرَظُ)</span> وَرَقُ السَّلَمِ يُدْبَغُ بِهِ.<span class="c5"> وَقِيلَ:</span> قِشْرُ الْبَلُّوطِ. وَ <span class="c2">(قُرَيْظَةُ)</span> وَالنَّضِيرُ قَبِيلَتَانِ مِنْ يَهُودِ خَيْبَرَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>